  "intent": "Execute an automated nucleic acid extraction protocol using the MGI Easy Nucleic Acid Extraction Kit with magnetic bead separation. Add 460\u00b5L lysis buffer to extraction wells, transfer 200\u00b5L samples and incubate 10 minutes. Perform magnetic separation for 5 minutes, remove 660\u00b5L supernatant, then execute three sequential wash steps with 300\u00b5L wash buffers and 4-minute magnetic separations. Air dry beads for 10 minutes, elute with 75\u00b5L RNase-free water using 8-cycle mixing, and transfer final 75\u00b5L eluate to output plate after 4-minute magnetic separation.",
